snippet.title: DEBENHAMS BEAUTY ADVENT CALENDAR 2019 UNBOXING - ONLY £45 WORTH £190 | AMBER HOWE
snippet.description:
Hey Babes!  I couldn't believe my luck when I noticed Debenhams had brought out a amazing beauty advent calendar this year featuring some incredible brands and products!

The calendar retails at £90 if purchased alone or if you purchase any other beauty product from the Debenhams beauty hall it is only £45 and has over £190 value!!!!

Buy yours here:

https://www.debenhams.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/prod_10701_10001_154330900499_-1#intcmp=christmasddn-christmas-gifts-the-debenhams-beauty-advent-calendar

*
I'm Amber and I make videos about all things beauty, fashion and lifestyle related! . I chat about my latest beauty, makeup and fashion finds in my hauls and reviews. I take you along with me from time to time, showing you my daily life in my vlogs!
